room_title: Escape room "Cabin 11" by Escape Room Virginia Peninsula in Newport News
review: Enjoyed the Camp themed room very much. The clues and riddles were very creative and challenging. I'm sure I'll be back.

room_title: Escape room "Cabin 11" by Escape Room Virginia Peninsula in Newport News
review: Was amazing and so much fun. We all had a blast. We escaped but the Cabin 11 room was tough.

room_title: Escape room "Cabin 11" by Escape Room Virginia Peninsula in Newport News
review: Went with a few friends. We all got to wear crazy hats while we did Cabin 11. It was super fun and challenging. My group finished with only about 5 min left!
